snippet.title: Harbinger - Tavern Area Early Look
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game here!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2859800/Harbinger/

Here's an early look at the tavern hub area for my next game Harbinger! It is very work-in-progress 
and subject to change and improvements before the game is released. Also, the game has a pixelated art style on both the textures and also a post process effect which pixelates the screen, youtube compression kind of makes it look blurry but it is much more sharp in-game. I hope you like it!

Check out my free retro FPS game on steam here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2421370/Cryptis
